<seg id="14">The feature of & FSView; consists of graphically represented nested order hierarchies with the help of a so-called Tree-Map. each object is represented by a rectangle whose area is proportional to its size. this size must have the property that the sum of the size of the subordinate objects of an object is smaller or equal to the size of the object.</seg>
